Revision history for Posy-Plugin-Pod
====================================

0.41 Sun 16 January 2005
------------------------

  * (16 Jan 2005) fix for multiple entries
  	It seems that the Pod::Simple::HTML object isn't really designed
  to be reset when it changes the source, so in order to make things work
  correctly on multiple POD entries, one needs to recreate the object
  each time.  Oh well.

0.40 Sat 15 January 2005
------------------------

  * (15 Jan 2005) splitting out from Posy core
